Patch summary:
Consolidate LineageOS Desktop Clang 22 compatibility fixes across Android source projects.
This patch keeps external libraries, bionic, Trusty, device/goldfish,
hardware/ril, and frameworks/native building with Clang 22 diagnostics that
are promoted to errors in the desktop ROM build. It also keeps Trusty's direct
Rust invocations aligned with Soong's Rust bootstrap environment.

